<p><strong>How is a Solar Return Ascendant interpreted?</strong></p>
<p>Keep in mind that it is not possible to do a Solar Return without first having the Natal Chart of the person in question, as the Natal Chart is the basis of the energetic structure of each individual.</p>
<p><strong>Cancer Ascendant in Solar Return</strong></p>
<p>A year marked by matters concerning family and home. Stability and a solid foundation will be sought firmly to feel protected. There may be a tendency to gain weight, possibly due to increased water retention. Affability and a more sensitive demeanor may be prominent. Increased contact with the public is possible. The Moon in Cancer in the 1st House will intensify everything related to the sign. In Taurus, one would seek suitable individuals to achieve performance at a certain level. In Scorpio or Capricorn, there is a risk of showing a cold and calculated interest in wealth and securing oneself.</p>
<p>The analysis of a solar return is seen in the 2nd and 3rd level of the astrology career.</p>
